129250c1181a6dd7dfc56b360cee77f3983130","tid":2204971,"uid":39722,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:48:52.000Z","msg":"Admin開個apple台，然後an狗返去玩具台就冇事"},{"pid":"55663bc7af9d2967f90108e3bd0ff23d4d05d9d1","tid":2204971,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T19:42:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f088e1565673e3cc8fc1a8f6eacd2f5a54a01a4","tid":2204971,"uid":146934,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T20:52:34.000Z","msg":"三大低賤生物<br />\n<br />\nAn狗<br />\n藍波狗<br />\n波台狗"},{"pid":"b023a0893cb9127964d8ee44fc516b1defc24387","tid":2204971,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:23:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-small\">連登既然開左「手機」台，點解唔索性開多個「筆電」台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2199725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2199725</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"5e66569dd4329a0b2d00652a0742c55c85078091","tid":2204971,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"開個apple 台啦"},{"pid":"0a8fd7f5d8762693329ce0a5bdfc7750104ec0e7","tid":2204971,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c6e6b7ae5db36f18747223d4c9d192dcfeba490","tid":2204971,"uid":154255,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:31:47.000Z","msg":"「手機」台點解有香港人出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"因為香港就係用｢手機｣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你喺哩度都可以捉到個當手機係支語嘅白痴仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手提電話 ➡️ 手機，哩個叫演變<br />\n當手機唔係淨係拎嚟打電話，叫&quot;手提電話&quot;已經唔再貼切<br />\n咪慢慢改叫做手機囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Jh_t2M8zlaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJh_t2M8zlaA&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=64b2307d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Jh_t2M8zlaA</a><br />\n1997年香港已經開始有手機哩個用法，係由台灣傳入<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av77139870/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav77139870%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=61575a53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av77139870/</a><br />\n而支那仲用緊手提電話<br />\n到底由幾時開始啲傻閪當晒手機係支語￼，明明係支那抄我哋改口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果所有用語演變都當支語，咁你一定仲用緊「番鬼佬涼茶」,「荷蘭水」同「的士高」啦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c9ea6926c5d8c6ae39810a1ce0d575b1a46fd3","tid":2204971,"uid":240069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"一堆tablet 係度仲荒謬<br />\n<br />\n電子錶, 耳機至少可以話係電話配件"},{"pid":"d3df2dcf649e1c42f28e27fd4ca74dad131f299f","tid":2204971,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73129250c1181a6dd7dfc56b360cee77f3983130","tid":2204971,"uid":39722,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T17:48:52.000Z","msg":"Admin開個apple台，然後an狗返去玩具台就冇事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"admin開個愛國台，apple用家啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7dcf2e35ac8e3d3eaf61cac56f1971266f721f","tid":2204971,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f088e1565673e3cc8fc1a8f6eacd2f5a54a01a4","tid":2204971,"uid":146934,"like":10,"dislike":5,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T20:52:34.000Z","msg":"三大低賤生物<br />\n<br />\nAn狗<br />\n藍波狗<br />\n波台狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用愛國apple情操最高尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46bf5b93a911893a1a27ba61a155e6546dc22f4","tid":2204971,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"開個arm台算啦，軟硬件越嚟越通用<b